#: selfdrive/ui/layouts/settings/toggles.py:175
msgid ""
"Longitudinal Control modes:<br>IQ.Pilot features are listed below:"
"<br><h4>IQ.Pilot End-to-End Longitudinal Control</h4><br>Let the driving "
"model control the gas and brakes. IQ.Pilot will drive as it thinks a human "
"would, including stopping for red lights and stop signs. Since the driving "
"model decides the speed to drive, the set speed will only act as an upper "
"bound. This feature is still being improved; mistakes should be expected."
"<br><h4>IQ.Dynamic</h4><br>Dynamically blends between adaptive cruise "
"behavior and end-to-end behavior based on scene/context.<br><h4>IQ.Standard</"
"h4><br>Uses standard traffic-aware cruise behavior for longitudinal control."
"<br><h4>New Driving Visualization</h4><br>The driving visualization will "
"transition to the road-facing wide-angle camera at low speeds to better show "
"some turns. The IQ.Pilot logo will also be shown in the top right corner."
msgstr ""
"纵向控制模式：<br>IQ.Pilot 功能如下：<br><h4>IQ.Pilot 端到端纵向控制</h4><br>"
"由驾驶模型控制油门与刹车,IQ.Pilot 会模拟人类驾驶方式行驶,包括在红灯和停车标"
"志前停车.由于行驶速度由驾驶模型决定,设定速度仅作为上限.此功能仍在优化中,"
"可能会出现失误.<br><h4>IQ.Dynamic</h4><br>根据场景/环境动态融合自适应巡航与"
"端到端控制逻辑.<br><h4>IQ.Standard</h4><br>采用标准的交通感知巡航逻辑进行纵"
"向控制.<br><h4>全新驾驶可视化</h4><br>低速时,驾驶可视化界面将切换为朝前的广"
"角摄像头画面,更清晰地显示转弯路况.IQ.Pilot 标识也将显示在右上角."

